bug.short_desc: Complex layouts in webkit results into stack size error

long_desc.thetext: Safari has a layoutproblem with the ColorPopup1 example. If you click "Open Popup" -> "Open ColorPopup" the color picker is layouted wrong (screenshot). The color selector alone however is working fine. E.g. in the ColorSelector1 example.

This is a known WebKit bug. The maximum stack size is only 100. All other browsers have a maximum stack size of about 1000.
http://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=4045
Won't fix (we cannot do anything here)
this is finally fixed in Webkit.
